# Lab 03 — PPO + PEFT Detoxification

----------------------------------------------------
## Overview
This lab explores an RLHF-style workflow using Proximal Policy Optimization (PPO) and PEFT/LoRA to guide a language model toward generating less toxic summaries.

The model used FLAN-T5 for dialogue summarization, a RoBERTa-based hate speech classifier as the reward model, and PPO for reinforcement learning optimization.

