## Workflow

The main workflow was:

1. Load and preprocess the DialogSum dataset
2. Create instruction-style summarization prompts
3. Create a local PEFT/LoRA adapter
4. Wrap the model with a PPO ValueHead
5. Create a frozen reference model
6. Load a RoBERTa-based hate speech reward model
7. Evaluate toxicity before PPO training
8. Run lightweight PPO fine-tuning
9. Evaluate toxicity after PPO training
10. Compare generated summaries qualitatively

