## Professional Takeaway

This lab helped me understand the basic workflow behind RLHF-style training:

1. Generate model outputs
2. Score outputs with a reward model
3. Use PPO to update the model policy
4. Compare the model before and after optimization

The experiment demonstrated how reinforcement learning and PEFT can be combined to influence LLM behavior in a more controlled and efficient way.

